taught me philosophy

00:05:47.900 --> 00:05:51.090
was in the business school
at Berkeley, a great man.

00:05:51.090 --> 00:05:52.920
And so he was a philosopher.

00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:55.280
So it was only natural
when I got through,

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:57.690
because I loved
engineering, but I

00:05:57.690 --> 00:05:59.470
